import React, { useState } from 'react'
import UpperNav from './upperNav/UpperNav'
import MiddleNav from './middleNav/MiddleNav'
import WelcomeBar from './welcomeBar'
import CategoriesBar from './categoriesBar/categoriesBar'
import { Icon } from 'react-icons-kit'
import {search, user, heart, cart } from 'react-icons-kit/icomoon'
import { ic_menu } from 'react-icons-kit/md/ic_menu'
import { cross } from 'react-icons-kit/icomoon/cross'
import Link from 'next/link'


function NavBar({ changeMenuClicked, categories, max_shown, links, home }) {

    return (
        <nav className="fixed flex flex-col w-full bg-white" >
            <UpperNav
                changeMenuClicked={changeMenuClicked}
                home={home}
                links={links}
            />
            <MiddleNav
                links={links}
            />
            <WelcomeBar textToDisplay="welcome" />
            <CategoriesBar max_shown={max_shown} categories={categories} />
        </nav>
    )
}

export default NavBar
